sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Client
    participant LLS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant Inline as GarakInlineEvalAdapter
    participant Remote as GarakRemoteEvalAdapter
    participant KFP as Kubeflow Pipelines API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KFPPod as KFP Pipeline Pod
    participant Target as Target Model (vLLM)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FilesAPI as Llama Stack Files API
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EvalHub as Eval-Hub Service
    participant Adapter as GarakAdapter Pod
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User, FilesAPI: Flow 1: Inline Scan Execution (Llama Stack)
    User->>LLS: POST /eval/run_benchmark<br/>Auth: Llama Stack auth
    LLS->>Inline: invoke eval provider (local)
    Inline->>Inline: garak subprocess<br/>(asyncio semaphore)
    Inline->>Target: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: API Key
    Target-->>Inline: Model response
    Inline->>FilesAPI: Upload artifacts (local)<br/>Reports, JSONL, HTML
    Inline-->>LLS: EvalResult (scores, artifacts)
    LLS-->>User: Benchmark results

    Note over User, FilesAPI: Flow 2: Remote KFP Scan Execution (Llama Stack)
    User->>LLS: POST /eval/run_benchmark<br/>Auth: Llama Stack auth
    LLS->>Remote: invoke eval provider
    Remote->>KFP: Create pipeline run<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    KFP->>KFPPod: Schedule 4-step pipeline
    KFPPod->>Target: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: API Key (from Secret)
    Target-->>KFPPod: Model response
    KFPPod->>FilesAPI: Upload artifacts<br/>Auth: None (in-cluster)
    loop Poll for completion
        User->>LLS: GET /eval/job_status
        LLS->>Remote: check status
        Remote->>KFP: GET /apis/v2beta1/runs/{id}<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        KFP-->>Remote: Run status
        Remote-->>LLS: Job status
        LLS-->>User: Status response
    end

    Note over EvalHub, OCI: Flow 3: Eval-Hub KFP Scan Execution
    EvalHub->>Adapter: Launch Job Pod<br/>ConfigMap mount (JobSpec)
    Adapter->>KFP: Create 6-step pipeline run<br/>Auth: SA Token
    KFP->>KFPPod: Schedule pipeline
    KFPPod->>KFPPod: validate → resolve_taxonomy
    KFPPod->>S3: Download custom taxonomy<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
    KFPPod->>Target: SDG model calls<br/>Auth: API Key
    KFPPod->>Target: Garak scan<br/>Auth: API Key (from /mnt/model-auth)
    Target-->>KFPPod: Model responses
    KFPPod->>S3: Upload results<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
    Adapter->>S3: Download results<br/>Auth: AWS IAM
    Adapter->>OCI: Push artifacts<br/>Auth: OCI auth
    Adapter->>EvalHub: Report status/metrics<br/>(sidecar HTTP)
